_sText:
A small, relatively simple map really...
Just something I thought would be a bit different and refreshing.
Both teams start on their own ship which will start moving 5 seconds after the round begins (including freeze time). From there on, you can jump to shore or stick to the ships.
There are 2 bomsites in the map. One in the bar at the middle, and one at the porch of the CT building.

All suggestions are welcome, and if you notice anything wrong with it, please let me know so I can fix it.

Fixed the damn door... I could have swore I made it a func_detail already.
Sorry for the inconvinience.
